Table.SCRIPT: Deep in the Amazon Rainforest is the city of Manaus, located in Brazil in [{South America}]. A big city in the middle of the rainforest is unique, but Manaus was built there for a [{reason}]. Manaus was built in a good place where two large rivers meet and become one. Many [{goods}] could be moved around and sold easily from Manaus. [{Rubber}] came from the rainforest, was moved along the river, and sold here. Manaus [{rapidly}] grew bigger and it soon became a [{center}] for business. Manaus is still an important city where [{electronics}] are made.
Table.TITLE: Manaus
